      "50_silver_coins": "one month living expenses (moderate)",
      "1_gold_coin": "a small house / half-year living expenses",
      "3_gold_coins": "high-grade weapon or magic equipment",
      "5+_gold_coins": "magic items, luxury mansions",
      "10+_gold_coins": "castles, estates"
    },
    "notes": "Everyday transactions use copper/silver coins. Gold coins are only used for high-value transactions. Pulling out gold coins in a rural village draws attention."
